{"tid":1220290,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"給香港人的一封信","createTime":"2019-06-14T03:35:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T12:22:51.000Z","uid":183971,"like":131,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"09f7c922df5871fb6dcdb32e54f45fad4dbe63b7","tid":1220290,"uid":183971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:35:27.000Z","msg":"各位親愛的信徒及非信徒：<br />\n<br />\n牧師我好滾動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望有更多人明白基督徒不是沉默的大多數<br />\n<br />\n其實好多事情上我們只是用一些靜態的方式來表現（例如祈禱）<br />\n<br />\n更加多謝有其他的基督徒用行動去行出來，面對警察向佢地唱詩歌。<br />\n<br />\n雖然可能你會話唱詩幾個小時係冇咩野，呢家係抗爭，但我地已經攞出認為係最好的野（例如教會的地方，人，物資等等）。 完全睇到基督徒的合一。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後請容許我用一句聖經作為總結：<br />\n<br />\n「只要你們行道，不要單單聽道，自己欺哄自己」<br />\n雅1:22<br />\n<br />\n希望大家16/6 唔會因爲父親節而少左人，而正正係因為父親節呢個咁有意義的日子。更加要行出來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我相信呢一個會係對世人來講係一個有力的見證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以上都係被人係夢遊時被紀錄低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n主的家奴<br />\n連登牧師"},{"pid":"e771e4f0221b06ae37c65b592e4e4a6f9b42c69c","tid":1220290,"uid":29270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:36:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ffea31c9b7f6062324e7a8708da1afa9278e3c1","tid":1220290,"uid":182715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:38:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f85f31c54221a0183d2ab1cfe4518ab146f8819","tid":1220290,"uid":183971,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:42:33.000Z","msg":"光照在黑暗裡，黑暗卻不接受光<br />\n<br />\n約翰福音1:5"},{"pid":"8a8322096febd67acf9955d7544986287e63b795","tid":1220290,"uid":88123,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:43:22.000Z","msg":"牧師<br />\n連登仔都感化到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2052a467b2f1042c3d3e729f69dd4e0b4d0b1321","tid":1220290,"uid":183971,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"8a8322096febd67acf9955d7544986287e63b795","tid":1220290,"uid":88123,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:43:22.000Z","msg":"牧師<br />\n連登仔都感化到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:48:06.000Z","msg":"考慮加入講道內容"},{"pid":"c023b6fcaad0b4bf2695311ac48bc08a323c95dc","tid":1220290,"uid":189484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:52:13.000Z","msg":"多謝你地"},{"pid":"5ea3b887442f7f9ba9572a50363a126baaa98619","tid":1220290,"uid":40439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:53:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2460322c26c1179b4d01cbc4c45180092468a1a","tid":1220290,"uid":127448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:58:16.000Z","msg":"多謝牧師，多謝教會支持學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f6e2ab798bdc4caa99da58985b251e83b5aa7dc","tid":1220290,"uid":183971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:59:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89c04f06923605d85ae3d450ecf96523c667f337","tid":1220290,"uid":18639,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T04:01:29.000Z","msg":"幫推 好多謝你地既付出<br />\n利申 非教徒 但都好想唱一句 sing hallelujah to the lord <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\